data.title: Dean's List
data.meta_description: Central Piedmont Community College Dean's List. Updated after each semester.
data.text:
To honor students in for-college-credit programs for outstanding academic achievement, the college publishes a Dean's List at the end of each term. The Dean's List recognizes students who achieved a 3.50 or greater grade point average (GPA) with no Incomplete ("I") or Withdraw ("W") grades and who have completed at least 12 hours of credit in courses numbered 100 through 299.

Jump to the Fall 2023 list.

For information from older lists, contact Amy Bruining or Karine Injaychock.
